<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tiān shǔ nǐ ya de shǔ nǐ 迦南811</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tiān shǔ nǐ ya de shǔ nǐ, wàn wù dōu shì nǐ qīn shǒu suǒ zào de.
 wǒ men de shēng mìng shì nǐ cì gěi de. wǒ men yào gǎn xiè nǐ.
 a tiān shàng de shén, wǒ men yī tóng jìng bài nǐ.
 a dú yī de shén, wǒ men yào chuán yáng nǐ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>811</hymn_number>
</song>